<title>SOUTH AFRICA: Opus says Moribo talks announcement soon.</title>
<headline>Opus says Moribo talks announcement soon.</headline>
<dateline>JOHANNESBURG 1997-07-07</dateline>
<text>
<p>South African gambling group Opus Investments Ltd said it was finalising a due diligence exercise on the acquisition of some of the leisure and sporting assets of Moribo Investments (Pty) Ltd.</p>
<p>Negotiations were continuing on the deal, which would see the black empowerment group taking a stake in the gambling company.</p>
<p>A company notice warned shareholders to exercise caution in their deals and said a detailed announcement would be made on completion of the talks.</p>
<p>--Johannesburg newsroom -27-11-482.1003</p>
